Description: ProB2 JavaFX animator and model checker
 ProB2-UI is the modern JavaFX user interface for the ProB animator, constraint
 solver and model checker. It supports B, Event-B, CSP-M, TLA+ and Z with
 interactive animation, model checking, LTL/CTL, trace recording and replay and
 visualisation.
 .
 The application is distributed as a self-contained multi-platform jar that
 bundles the JavaFX runtime and downloads the matching ProB kernel on first use.
